Thank you to Qualcomm for sponsoring this video! Learn more about Snapdragon 8 Elite and Snapdragon X Elite:
https://www.qualcomm.com/products/mobile/snapdragon/smartphones/snapdragon-8-series-mobile-platforms/snapdragon-8-elite-mobile-platform
https://www.qualcomm.com/products/mobile/snapdragon/laptops-and-tablets

I've spent the last year since Snapdragon Summit learning about and testing Snapdragon-powered laptops, and the progress has been legit. From the high-end Snapdragon X Elite to the surprisingly capable Snapdragon X Plus powered $850 IdeaPad 5X, these devices are added a lot of competition to what we expect from Windows laptops. In this video, I break down my honest experience with battery life, performance, and app compatibility - sharing why I keep reaching for these machines over "traditional" laptops.
